you have to get out of prison someday.

44:20.240 --> 44:21.659
You said you would trust me.

44:22.242 --> 44:24.912
You think I would have done this
if I had any other choice?

44:24.995 --> 44:27.206
Hellman shoved heroin down my throat. And by that I mean I had to swallow it
and shit it out.

44:29.958 --> 44:31.502
