45:01.615 --> 45:03.117
<i>How's work?</i>

45:06.495 --> 45:07.496
So lame.

45:07.579 --> 45:08.622
You wanna tell me about it?

45:12.292 --> 45:14.628
My father won't let me
come see you on Friday.

45:16.839 --> 45:20.259
Oh, Bill. Should I send someone
to fuck him up?

45:21.844 --> 45:23.971
I'm sorry I won't be able to be there.

45:26.473 --> 45:28.058
At least we have a way to talk now.

45:30.811 --> 45:34.940
Yes. At least we have that.

45:45.909 --> 45:47.619
This is GED. You're not signed up.

45:47.995 --> 45:49.538
I know. School sucks.

45:51.290 --> 45:53.000
What other programs you got?

45:57.212 --> 45:59.590
Looks like the only one
you haven't been to yet is crochet.

46:00.758 --> 46:02.760
