is to get out of Florida.

46:05.429 --> 46:06.388
School does suck.

46:08.223 --> 46:11.018
Nice to meet you, Ms...

46:11.727 --> 46:14.396
Tiffany. I mean, Doggett.

46:14.980 --> 46:16.648
All right, well, come on,
Ms. Tiffany Doggett,

46:16.732 --> 46:18.817
let's talk about why school sucks.

46:18.901 --> 46:20.277
Everyone.

46:20.360 --> 46:21.528
School.

46:22.571 --> 46:24.239
That's why we're all here, right?

46:26.533 --> 46:30.662
Why does school

46:30.746 --> 46:33.916
suck so bad?

46:36.418 --> 46:37.503
Anyone?

46:38.170 --> 46:41.089
