46:41.381 --> 46:42.299
Homework.

46:42.382 --> 46:43.675
Tests.

46:43.759 --> 46:47.095
I actually really liked school,
but my socioeconomic circumstances

46:47.179 --> 46:49.306
dictated that I drop out
to earn my keep, so...

46:49.389 --> 46:51.183
