who think they're cute." But...

48:07.801 --> 48:11.179
Hey. Are you here for class?
I guess it's never too late.

48:11.555 --> 48:12.806
Can I talk to you outside?

48:12.890 --> 48:14.266
...there.

48:14.349 --> 48:19.479
They are. They are.
T-H-E-Y-apostrophe-R-E.

48:19.563 --> 48:20.439
Good.

48:20.522 --> 48:22.774
Hey. Sorry about that.
I wasn't saying that you're old.

48:23.859 --> 48:28.071
Sometimes, my mouth and my noggin
don't work together like they should.

48:28.655 --> 48:31.199
It's almost like I have
a brain injury or some...

48:31.283 --> 48:33.327
Shit.

48:33.410 --> 48:35.913
Starting over.
It's been a while since I've seen you.

48:35.996 --> 48:38.248
Maybe because I've been in the SHU
for a very long time.

48:40.083 --> 48:41.752
In my defense,
you told me not to come visit.

48:41.835 --> 48:43.462
