48:45.088 --> 48:46.465
I need you to get me one.

48:46.548 --> 48:49.927
Damn. And here I thought
you were all straight angles and shit.

48:51.845 --> 48:52.930
You gonna get me a phone or no?

48:54.306 --> 48:55.307
Totes.

48:56.433 --> 48:59.770
Yeah, uh... Hey, and since it's you,
